#: ../../A/ASCIIbetical-order.rst:5
msgid "ASCIIbetical order"
msgstr "ASCIIbetical order"

#: ../../A/ASCIIbetical-order.rst:7
msgid "/as´kee·be'·t\\@·kl or´dr/, adj\\.,n\\."
msgstr "/as´kee·be'·t\\@·kl or´dr/, 形容詞,名詞"

#: ../../A/ASCIIbetical-order.rst:9
msgid ""
"Used to indicate that data is sorted in ASCII collated order rather than "
"alphabetical order. This lexicon is sorted in something close to "
"ASCIIbetical order, but with case ignored and entries beginning with non-"
"alphabetic characters moved to the beginning."
msgstr ""
"データがアルファベット順ではなくASCIIの照合順で並んでいることを示すのに使う。この用語集も、ASCIIbetical "
"orderに近い順序で並んでいるが、大文字小文字は無視し、英字以外の文字で始まる項目は先頭に移してある。"
